11. What the prototype should avoid

Avoid turning into:

a generic forum
a spreadsheet dashboard
an eventbrite clone
a social feed full of posts
a member directory with little meaning
a full marketplace flow
a productivity app for admin labor

The prototype should stay centered on:
orientation, overlap, participation, and legibility.

